                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="Isa-065-fn1" type="footnote">ADub.III.83: <emph>banjat</emph>;
                            a scribal error. | F305-90: <emph>bajat</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Isa-065-fn2" type="footnote">ADub.III.83: Isaiah 65:9 is
                            omitted by the copyist. The reconstruction is based on the Hebrew
                            original and F305-90: <emph>Da čyɣaryrmyn Jaʿaqovdan urluq da Juhudadan
                                ḿeŕaśĺav́č́u tavlarymny da ḿeŕaśĺarĺar sajlanmyšlarym da
                                qullarym toḥtarlar anda</emph>.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
